    <data key="d0">Epsagon Serverless Telemetry Processing &amp; Analytics Engine</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzM_d7ZvzUE</data>
    <data key="d2">Handles billions of customer lambda invocations monthly. Uses a split fast-path (Aurora) and analytical-path (Firehose/S3/Athena) pattern. Leverages Kinesis to protect Aurora from connection overloading.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, compute_intensive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
